{"title":"柳林庄上送公粮","authors":["芦甸"],"dates":[{"year":1948,"month":10,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳林庄上送公粮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芦甸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣声响呀响镗镗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳林庄的群众聚集在南场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的＠蹴有的坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娃娃们爬在柳树上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"★"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农会主任拿着旱烟袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面比划一面讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“前方后方一条总战线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军老百姓一条心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打过黄河打长江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家赶快交公粮。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"★"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人群中立起刘老汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过众人往前站；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱养种一辈子地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打下粮食往地主家里扛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主住楼房吃白面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱端的一碗稀糊汤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今自己的庄子自己的地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己的粮食自己的仓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪辈子也没囤过谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大闺女上轿头一趟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁给咱这好光景？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙往回想一想………”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"★"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张大娘两手胸前抱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圪扭圪扭走到场中央："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“俺提议都碾早谷子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"米要一粒一粒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不带沙子不粘糠。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"★"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“同意张大娘！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“拥护张大娘！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"★"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“俺还有个小意见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布袋要顶底能相照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮面脚底要一样………”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙听了这句话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉们笑得摸胡子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女们笑得直叫娘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“张大娘呀张大娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你还是老脑筋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是封建老财们办的事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众哪有那号坏思想。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张大娘呀张大娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑得满脸放红光………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳林庄里人人忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳林庄的牲口转的慌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳林庄里明地黑夜忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到东头，碾盘沙沙沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来西头，扇车嗡嗡响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大街小巷都走遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家户户都忙公粮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮是柳林庄的一盏灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照见柳林庄的碾院明亮亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汉们推碾娘们扇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有说有笑碾公粮………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"★"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满天星斗满地霜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳林庄的群众送公粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑娃一心想往头里赶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛上布袋跑南场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一看众人早来到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装的装，量的量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙煞咱们老村长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驴呀骡呀嚎嚎叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"足足拖到半里长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布袋驮上牲口背，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声吆喝出了庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞭梢空中“叭叭”响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嗒嗒”“咧咧”翻过了柳林岗……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}